---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="express-main-container">
    <section class="express-header">
      <svg class="express-icon" role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="color:#444"><title>Express</title><path fill="currentColor" d="M24 18.588a1.529 1.529 0 01-1.895-.72l-3.45-4.771-.5-.667-4.003 5.444a1.466 1.466 0 01-1.802.708l5.158-6.92-4.798-6.251a1.595 1.595 0 011.9.666l3.576 4.83 3.596-4.81a1.435 1.435 0 011.788-.668L21.708 7.9l-2.522 3.283a.666.666 0 000 .994l4.804 6.412zM.002 11.576l.42-2.075c1.154-4.103 5.858-5.81 9.094-3.27 1.895 1.489 2.368 3.597 2.275 5.973H1.116C.943 16.447 4.005 19.009 7.92 17.7a4.078 4.078 0 002.582-2.876c.207-.666.548-.78 1.174-.588a5.417 5.417 0 01-2.589 3.957 6.272 6.272 0 01-7.306-.933 6.575 6.575 0 01-1.64-3.858c0-.235-.08-.455-.134-.666A88.33 88.33 0 010 11.577zm1.127-.286h9.654c-.06-3.076-2.001-5.258-4.59-5.278-2.882-.04-4.944 2.094-5.071 5.264z"/></svg>
      <h1>Express.js</h1>
      <p>(Framework minimalista para Node.js)</p>
    </section>
    <section class="express-content">
      <h2>¿Qué podés encontrar acá?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fundamentos y estructura de Express</li>
        <li>Rutas, middlewares y controladores</li>
        <li>Ejemplos de APIs y servidores</li>
        <li>Recursos y enlaces útiles</li>
      </ul>
      <blockquote class="express-quote">"Express simplifica el desarrollo de servidores en Node.js."</blockquote>
      <a href="/blog" class="back-main-btn">Volver al inicio</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
.express-main-container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2.5rem 1rem 2.5rem 1rem;
  font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
}
.express-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
}
.express-icon {
  width: 54px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  display: block;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  color: #444;
}
.express-header h1 {
  font-size: 2.1rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  color: #444;
}
.express-header p {
  font-size: 1.13rem;
  color: var(--color-text, #444);
  max-width: 500px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.express-content h2 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  color: #444;
}
.express-content ul {
  margin: 0 0 1.2rem 1.2rem;
  padding: 0;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.express-content li {
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.express-quote {
  margin: 1.5rem 0 0 0;
  padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
  background: #f3f3f3;
  border-left: 4px solid #444;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #222;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.back-main-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 2rem auto 0 auto;
  padding: 0.7rem 2.1rem;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #444 0%, #888 100%);
  color: #fff;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #4442;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s, transform 0.13s;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-align: center;
}
.back-main-btn:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #888 0%, #444 100%);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px #4444;
  transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.04);
  color: #fff;
}
@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
  .express-header h1 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  .express-main-container {
    padding: 1.2rem 0.3rem 1.5rem 0.3rem;
  }
}
</style>
